BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the report include, at a minimum, how public
school systems can modify their operations in response to declining enrollment in order to
provide the best possible educational outcomes for their students and any state-level action
that should be taken to support school systems facing these challenges.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
state superintendent of education.
